Sutwarden: Foes of the Free People
Foes of the Free Peoples found at Sutwarden should be defeated in order protect those within the Wildwood.
Foes can be found at Sutwarden in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should defeat foes at Sutwarden.
Foes of the Free Peoples have claimed the tower of Sutwarden within the Wildwood. Defeating their numbers here will assist in returning safety to the Wildwood.
